definitions.definition: A blend of components that has been mixed in advance of use or of further processing.
A manufactured beverage consisting of alcohol and soft drink , milk or other non-alcoholic drinks; an alcopop .

main_definition: A blend of components that has been mixed in advance of use or of further processing.
